Team 1391, The Metal Moose, is proud to release our engineering notebook for the 2025 season! This season, we had a unique robot archetype featuring a hopper, and an arm for extra reach when scoring on the reef. Our engineering notebook features our decision making process, including prototypes, iterations, and inspiration.

Our robot, Anemone is able to‚Ä¶ Àñ¬∞ìáºìÇÉ ìàíìè∏

  • Score on L1, L2, L3 & L4
  • Get coral from the source
  • Pick up algae from ground and reef
  • Score algae in the barge and processor
  • Deep climb!!

Notebook is linked here!

1920√ó1280 205 KB

Our season‚Äôs recap:

  • Week 3: Captain of Alliance 3 @ Springside Chestnut Hill | Eliminated in Match 13 of playoffs | Excellence in Engineering Award

  • Week 5: 1st pick of Alliance 2 @ Centennial | FInalists | Gracious Professionalism Award

  • DCMP: 2nd pick of Alliance 3 | Eliminated in Match 13 of playoffs

We also qualified and competed in the Curie Division of the FIRST Championship!
